702004f-a.title: Bronx: Wales Avenue - 150th Street (East)
702004f-a.text:
568 ad 566 Wales Avenue, at, and adjoining the S.E. corner
of E. 150th Street. The corner house, No. 558, is the Lithuanian-
American Democratic Club. Also shown (left) is the southside of
E. 150th Street.
June 25, 1938.
P. L. Sperr
